ch item can have unique powers, belong to a set, feature a runic word or a gem, making the number of combinations greater than in other hack'n slash games. Stats are also randomized and tiered. A consumable-based customization system is also available.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/69b6d9247396bb77da2cecac40822aec.poster.avif?t=1764701708\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/69b6d9247396bb77da2cecac40822aec.webm?t=1764701708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Talent Trees:</strong> Each fragment of Ortharion gives you a point in talent trees, allowing for further customization of your character. The talent trees are specific to each class, with some talents completely altering gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/3af95e7c47459f9803afbf8c4254dfd9.poster.avif?t=1764701708\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/3af95e7c47459f9803afbf8c4254dfd9.webm?t=1764701708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Competitive Modes:</strong> The game has been designed with a ranking system. You need to accumulate points and can compare them with friends or the community through a seasonal system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High-Level Content:</strong> Participate in multiple high-level systems while engaging in the campaign, boss arenas, monster waves, random dungeons, objective protection, and more.   <br>   </p>",
